You need to tell spring to use method name as key. You can use SPEL for this. Here is the [doc][1] with various other options.


  [1]: https://docs.spring.io/spring/docs/3.1.x/spring-framework-reference/html/cache.html

You can use two cache with different name:

    @Bean
